LocLongDescription="Create an elemental barrier which degrades the next <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_NUMBER_OF_ATTACKS/></font> incoming hits to grazes. Direct attacks on the barrier return the damage psionically to the attacker. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Create an elemental barrier which reduces the next <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_NUMBER_OF_ATTACKS/></font> hits to grazes and returns damage to the attacker. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
