[Warden_BD_GrantImbueAmmoCharges X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Create Astral Bullet"
LocLongDescription="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced bullet(s) and the ability to create additional bullets every <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_COOLDOWN/></font> turns using <font color='#b6b3e3'>flow</font> action points. Attacks with the bullet deal +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignore armor & shields and bypass sustained units. They may only be fired in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font> and cannot critically hit."
LocHelpText="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced bullet(s) and the ability to create additional bullets every <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_COOLDOWN/></font> turns using <font color='#b6b3e3'>flow</font> action points. Attacks with the bullet deal +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignore armor & shields and bypass sustained units. They may only be fired in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font> and cannot critically hit."
LocFlyOverText="Create Astral Bullet"

