LocLongDescription="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced strike(s) and the ability to channel energy into the Warden's sword to carry out additional strikes every <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_COOLDOWN/></font> turns using <font color='#b6b3e3'>flow</font> action points. The attack does +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignores armor & shields and bypasses sustained units. It may only be used in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font> and cannot critically hit."
LocHelpText="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced strike(s) and the ability to channel energy into the Warden's sword to carry out additional strikes every <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_COOLDOWN/></font> turns using <font color='#b6b3e3'>flow</font> action points. The attack does +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignores armor & shields and bypasses sustained units. It may only be used in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font> and cannot critically hit."
