LocHelpText="Perform a psionically enhanced sword attack. The attack does +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignores armor & shields and bypasses sustained units but cannot critically hit. Requires <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>."
