LocHelpText="Place a large psionic ward on the ground. Non-robotic enemies are disoriented for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:DEFENSIVE_WARD_DISORIENT_TURNS/></font> turns and receive <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:DEFENSIVEWARD_DAMAGE/></font> psionic damage if they remain inside the ward at the end of the turn. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:DEFENSIVEWARD_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
