[Warden_BD_Tide X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Tide"
LocLongDescription="Create a psionic shockwave that pushes back & damages non-flying enemies, ignoring cover & armour. Deals <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_DAMAGE/></font> damage in a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_AREA_OF_EFFECT/></font> tile radius around the warden and stuns all enemies for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_STUN_DURATION/></font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Knock down & damage non-flying enemies, ignoring cover & armour. Deals <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_DAMAGE/></font> damage in a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_AREA_OF_EFFECT/></font> tile radius around the warden. Stuns for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_STUN_DURATION/></font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Tide"

[Warden_BD_Consume X2AbilityTemplate]
