LocLongDescription="Cleanse all mental and active damage-over-time effects from XCOM soldiers in the area of effect & provide them with immunity for 1 turn. Add <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_MULTIPLIER/></font> damage per turn remaining of each effect, to the Warden's next attack. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Cleanse all mental and active damage-over-time effects from XCOM soldiers in the area of effect & provide them with immunity for 1 turn. Add <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_MULTIPLIER/></font> damage per turn remaining of each effect, to the Warden's next attack. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Consume"

